[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0841","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0841.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0576","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16246,\"outputTokens\":37,\"totalTokens\":16283}}","description":"Windows NT 文件审核策略存在安全缺陷，系统未对安全关键文件或目录的访问操作记录审计日志，无论访问成功或失败均不生成任何事件记录。未经身份认证的远程或本地攻击者可利用该漏洞访问、篡改敏感系统文件而不留下任何审计痕迹，导致安全事件无法被检测和追溯。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，攻击者只需具备对目标系统文件的基本访问权限即可触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0576"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.873","remediation":"在 Windows NT 本地安全策略（Local Security Policy）中启用\"审核对象访问\"（Audit object access），审核成功和失败事件；在 %SystemRoot%、%SystemRoot%\\System32 等安全关键目录上配置 SACL 系统访问控制列表，确保对关键文件和目录的所有访问均被记录到安全日志中；定期检查事件查看器安全日志以监控异常访问。由于 Windows NT 已结束生命周期，建议迁移到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2022）以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0576","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0576","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0576.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3gh3-crhx-q3jq/GHSA-3gh3-crhx-q3jq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0576.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87898/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000133.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e2f73fd4-247a-4b46-b8bb-c1a20c030c99.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0841.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0840","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0575","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全审计策略配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统用户审计策略存在配置缺失漏洞，系统未对登录与注销、文件与对象访问、用户权限使用、用户与组管理、安全策略变更、系统重启与关机以及进程跟踪等关键安全事件记录成功或失败日志。该漏洞影响所有采用默认审计配置的 Windows NT 系统，攻击条件为系统审计策略未正确启用事件记录。攻击者可利用此漏洞进行未经授权的访问、权限提升或配置篡改等恶意操作，且所有行为均不会在安全日志中留下记录，导致安全管理员无法通过审计日志检测入侵事件、追溯攻击来源或进行事后取证分析，严重削弱了系统的安全监控与事件响应能力。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0575"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.760","remediation":"在 Windows NT 中打开「用户管理器」→「策略」→「审核」，勾选\"审核这些事件\"并至少启用\"登录及注销\"\"文件及对象访问\"\"用户权限的使用\"\"用户及组管理\"\"安全策略更改\"\"重新启动、关机及系统\"的成功与失败审核，运行 `auditpol /enable` 或重启使策略生效；对无法立即配置的域环境，通过域控制器组策略统一下发审核策略，并定期导出安全日志至集中日志服务器留存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0575","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0575.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x5gf-jr5f-x67g/GHSA-x5gf-jr5f-x67g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0575.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87880/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0840.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0838","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0572","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 2000 .reg 文件关联注册表木马注入漏洞","description":"Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统默认将 .reg 文件与注册表编辑器（regedit）关联，攻击者可构造包含恶意键值的 .reg 特洛伊木马文件，诱骗本地已登录用户双击执行，从而在用户权限下将恶意数据写入系统注册表，造成配置篡改、权限提升或持久化后门。该漏洞影响所有启用此默认关联的 Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统，攻击需本地用户主动打开恶意文件，属本地社会工程类风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0572"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.637","remediation":"建议将 Windows NT/2000 升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019/2022）。如无法立即升级，可通过修改文件关联将 .reg 文件默认打开方式从 regedit.exe 更改为记事本（notepad.exe），或通过组策略和注册表禁用 .reg 文件执行，并提醒用户不要打开来历不明的 .reg 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/178","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0572","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0572.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267/GHSA-rf7x-vm9v-6267.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0572.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000131.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0838.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0825","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0562","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10853,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10874}}","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0（含 SP1 至 SP5）的注册表允许未通过身份认证的远程用户借助空会话（Null Session）建立匿名连接并远程访问注册表数据，而无需具备管理员权限。该漏洞影响所有启用默认安全配置、开放 139/445 端口且允许空会话连接的 Windows NT 4.0 系统。攻击者只需与目标主机建立空会话（无需用户名与口令），即可通过远程注册表服务读取、枚举甚至修改敏感配置信息，进而获取系统账户、共享及服务配置等关键信息，为进一步的权限提升与入侵创造条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0562"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.693","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 及以上版本补丁，在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\LSA 中将 RestrictAnonymous 设为 1（或 2）以禁止空会话枚举，并停止/禁用\"Remote Registry\"服务（将启动类型改为禁用），同时在边界防火墙阻断 TCP 139/445 端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1023","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19372","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0562","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0562.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a20296d4b03dbd5c5991115b8296a9f2b947592/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/29e1987d1015171e4c9687edfd31170902b59c7a/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_registry_access.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0562.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f335152f-46ff-480a-9493-351c891d7140.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x7000/6830/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0825.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0814","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0550","title":"路由器路由表信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0550 是一个路由器信息泄露漏洞，由于路由器未对路由表查询请求进行访问控制，攻击者可通过发送 SNMP GetRequest 等协议报文从任意远程主机获取路由器的完整路由表信息。该漏洞影响早期缺乏安全加固的路由器设备，攻击者无需任何认证凭据即可远程读取路由条目，从而获知网络拓扑结构、内部网络地址分配及流量转发路径等敏感信息。攻击者可利用获取的路由信息进一步实施中间人攻击、流量劫持或针对性网络入侵，对网络基础设施安全构成严重威胁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0550"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.973","remediation":"立即升级路由器固件至最新版本，在所有接口上启用路由协议认证机制（RIPv2 使用明文/MD5 认证，OSPF 启用 MD5 认证，EIGRP 使用预共享密钥认证），并在面向外部网络的接口上配置访问控制列表（ACL）限制路由更新报文的来源地址，同时通过 `passive-interface` 命令在不需要发送路由更新的接口上禁用路由协议广播，防止攻击者嗅探或伪造路由信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0550","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0550.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/476c79e4154073134b6998fc7a1fcba149340485/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0550.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0550","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3950bef6f70c411ea08c8b2f1665dbd7d38277bd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0550.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0550.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcx3-6934-f759/GHSA-wcx3-6934-f759.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0550.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86061/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0814.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0803","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0535","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10780,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10800}}","description":"Windows NT 系统账户密码策略存在安全配置不当的问题，具体表现为密码最小长度过短、密码最长使用期限过长或密码历史记录不足等安全关键设置不合理。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 操作系统，攻击者利用这些弱密码策略，可通过暴力破解或字典攻击的方式更容易地猜测用户密码，从而获得系统未授权访问权限。管理员应修改默认密码策略设置，强制要求复杂密码并缩短更换周期以缓解风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0535"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.003","remediation":"打开「本地安全策略」(secpol.msc) → 账户策略 → 密码策略，将\"密码必须符合复杂性要求\"设为已启用，\"密码长度最小值\"设为至少12个字符，\"密码最长使用期限\"设为90天以内，\"强制密码历史\"设为记住24个密码；同时进入\"账户锁定策略\"将\"账户锁定阈值\"设为5次无效登录。对域环境通过组策略(gpmc.msc)在 Default Domain Policy 中统一下发，并执行 gpupdate /force 立即生效。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0535","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/442e3d0f3c777e02c70fc200a453fe1f1f8a2431/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0535.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0535","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0535.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0535.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-96cf-gc7m-wf44/GHSA-96cf-gc7m-wf44.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0535.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86049/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000130.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0803.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0802","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0534","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9176,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10859}}","description":"Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统存在用户权限分配不当的安全配置缺陷，部分普通用户账户被错误地授予了本应仅限管理员的高危特权，例如\"作为系统动作\"\"加载设备驱动\"\"调试程序\"\"恢复文件\"\"取得对象所有权\"\"远程关机\"等。攻击者只需先获取目标主机的本地普通用户登录权限，即可滥用这些过度授权的特权执行本地权限提升，绕过系统安全限制并以 SYSTEM 等高权限身份运行任意操作，进而完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响所有采用默认权限配置、未做最小权限加固的 Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统，易被本地已认证用户利用来破坏系统完整性与安全性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0534"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.877","remediation":"登录域控制器或本地安全策略控制台，依次打开「本地安全策略 → 本地策略 → 用户权限分配」，将\"作为系统操作、增加配额、创建永久对象、调试程序、替换进程令牌、取得所有权\"等敏感特权从普通用户/Everyone 组中移除，仅保留给 Administrators 与 SYSTEM。对 Windows NT 4.0 升级至 Service Pack 6a，Windows 2000 升级至 Service Pack 4，并通过组策略统一下发修正后的用户权限模板，定期审计特权分配以防止权限滥用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0534","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/442e3d0f3c777e02c70fc200a453fe1f1f8a2431/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0534.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0534","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0534.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0534.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wj4c-w2hq-86g5/GHSA-wj4c-w2hq-86g5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0534.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000129.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84432/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0802.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0782","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0525","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9086,\"outputTokens\":16,\"totalTokens\":10766}}","description":"该漏洞源于系统对 IP 路由跟踪（traceroute）功能的访问控制不当，未限制可发起 traceroute 请求的源地址范围。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可从任意主机向目标系统发送 traceroute 数据包，无需凭据即可获取目标网络的路径信息和中间路由节点，从而暴露内部网络拓扑结构。该漏洞影响配置不当的操作系统及网络设备，攻击者仅需目标系统网络可达即可利用，通过标准 traceroute 工具即可完成探测，为后续针对性攻击提供网络情报支持。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0525"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.923","remediation":"在受影响的路由器上禁用源路由功能，并通过访问控制列表（ACL）限制 ICMP traceroute 的访问来源。首先在全局配置模式下执行 no ip source-route 禁用 IP 源路由，然后在入站接口上应用 ACL 阻止未经授权的主机发送 traceroute 请求，仅允许受信任的管理网段发起。同时将设备升级至 Cisco 已修复此问题的 IOS 版本，或在防火墙层面阻断外部对 ICMP type 11（time exceeded）的流量，以进一步降低网络拓扑被外部探测的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0525","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0525.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ce36d0de2f3ddd1d56c222c398df994c8c331b1/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0525.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0525","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0525.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0525.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qvxm-qx8p-cvx4/GHSA-qvxm-qx8p-cvx4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0525.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86047/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0782.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0778","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0778.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0521","title":"Sun NIS 网域名称可猜测信息泄露漏洞","description":"NIS（网络信息服务，原名 Yellow Pages）协议存在安全设计缺陷，其域名通常为固定格式或可被轻易猜测。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过爆破或猜测 NIS 域名后，向目标系统的 ypserv 服务发送请求，获取 passwd、shadow、hosts 等关键映射信息。成功利用可导致用户密码哈希、主机配置等敏感数据泄露，为后续横向移动和权限提升创造有利条件。该漏洞影响所有启用 NIS 机制的系统（主要为 Unix/Linux 环境），属于经典的敏感信息泄露漏洞。修复措施包括限制 NIS 服务网络暴露面、使用 ypsec 安全机制或迁移至 LDAP 等更安全的替代方案。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0521"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.360","remediation":"将 NIS 域名设置为难以猜测的复杂字符串（至少 16 位，含大小写字母和数字），切勿使用默认或与组织信息相关的域名。在 /etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny 中限制能访问 NIS 服务的客户端 IP 范围，仅允许受信网段。如条件允许，建议迁移至 LDAP/Kerberos 等更安全的集中认证方案替代 NIS。iptables 层面仅放行必要端口（111/TCP/UDP 的 portmap 及 834/TCP/UDP 的 ypserv）的白名单来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-13.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0778.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0772","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0772.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0518","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9092,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10779}}","description":"Windows 95 系统的 NETBIOS/SMB 共享密码存在可被猜测的弱点，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过暴力破解或弱口令字典尝试，获取目标系统共享资源的访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows 95 及基于 NETBIOS/SMB 协议进行文件共享的早期 Windows 系统，攻击者只需能够连接到目标主机的 SMB 服务即可发起猜测，无需事先获取任何凭据，可能导致敏感文件被非法访问或篡改。建议用户为共享资源设置强密码策略，并限制 SMB 服务的网络访问范围以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0518"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.983","remediation":"在 Windows 95 网络中禁用不必要的\"文件和打印机共享\"服务，并为所有共享资源设置不少于8位且含大小写字母与数字的强口令；通过防火墙或路由器屏蔽 139/445 端口的入站 SMB 连接，或在网卡属性中仅绑定 TCP/IP 而不绑定\"Microsoft 网络上的文件与打印机共享\"以彻底关闭 NETBIOS 共享。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0518","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d4a574a76aebe4c90e3ed9125b2a8b9cb55a2a89/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0518.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0518","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0518.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cd1e3d0adf029810963282884bd6480e52b853ac/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0518.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6xr3-qh8w-2p53/GHSA-6xr3-qh8w-2p53.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0518.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7a85a2b3-bd49-4254-b1c3-56e043b6ceb5.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0772.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0771","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0771.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0517","title":"HP-UX SNMP 默认团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统上的 SNMP 服务使用了默认、为空或缺失的团体名（如常见的 \"public\"），导致攻击者无需有效凭证即可访问 SNMP 代理。该漏洞影响启用了 SNMP 服务且未修改默认配置的 HP-UX 主机，攻击条件为攻击者能通过网络访问目标主机的 UDP 161 端口。利用方式是通过发送带有默认团体名的 SNMP 请求，读取系统信息、网络配置、用户账户等敏感数据，可能造成信息泄露，CVSS 评分 5.9，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0517"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.790","remediation":"修改 SNMP community name 为复杂强密码，禁止使用默认值 public 或空字符串；如业务无需 SNMP 服务，直接禁用或卸载相关 SNMP 代理进程；在网络层面通过防火墙或 ACL 限制 UDP 161 端口的访问源，仅允许受信任的管理主机访问；升级至操作系统厂商发布的安全补丁版本，确保 SNMP 配置符合最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0517","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-244","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-244/","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0517.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/10323cb4135457b41074412d623aa2116c4e1200/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0517.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0517","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/0e18153fbb4123e7b766fcd8c28227fcde5a3816/1999/README.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/5a9570703da14a2b5eac448afa9c83878dd7f663/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0517.json","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/cd275183e69131386d0c86c5a1716b6a67ff7687/references/CVE-1999-0517-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0517.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wvmj-jgmg-4ghq/GHSA-wvmj-jgmg-4ghq.json","https://github.com/jacobdjwilson/awesome-annual-security-reports/blob/f0f80f6f91645a9b6c6e9d7233a009a7ac3a809a/Markdown%20Conversions/2025/Edgescan-Vulnerability-Statistics-Report-2025.md","https://github.com/ialejandrozalles/InvestigacionAplicacionCVE-1999-0517"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0771.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0765","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0765.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0511","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 IP 转发默认启用信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统默认或错误配置启用了 IP 转发功能，导致非路由器或防火墙的普通主机充当网络层转发节点。远程攻击者可利用此配置缺陷，通过该主机转发数据包绕过网络访问控制策略，实现内网探测、中间人攻击或信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 9.1，危害等级严重。修复建议为在非路由场景下禁用 IP 转发功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0511"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.007","remediation":"在非路由器的 Windows NT/2000 系统上，通过注册表将 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\IPEnableRouter` 值设为 0，或通过网络连接属性取消勾选「启用 IP 转发」。同时建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以获得更完善的安全机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0511","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0511.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0511","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/5a9570703da14a2b5eac448afa9c83878dd7f663/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0511.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/78eafd4564fbf54df959d50d6817c30fd8606422/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3fwm-5x3q-64xf/GHSA-3fwm-5x3q-64xf.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0511.json","https://github.com/Hurley2017/mulval_updated/blob/eeb3da1975075e62db42cbfde5b4a8a3e9f35654/CustomTests/HomeWiFi/vulInfo.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83204/info.html","https://github.com/hadousoftware/base-images/blob/ab6afc9661bbd001d8be8fdc4ac1a3fdd8d1e824/base/abi/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0765.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0764","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0764.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0510","title":"路由器或防火墙 IP源路由绕过漏洞","description":"IP 源路由选项（Loose Source and Record Route / Strict Source Routing）允许数据包发送方指定途经路径。当路由器或防火墙未正确过滤携带源路由选项的 IP 数据包时，远程攻击者可绕过正常的路由策略和访问控制规则，伪造可信源地址，将数据包强制路由至本不可达的内部网络，进而实施网络探测、中间人攻击或越权访问。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS v2.0 评分 7.5，危害等级高。缓解措施包括在网络边界设备上禁用 IP 源路由选项的转发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0510"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.890","remediation":"在路由器或防火墙上禁用 IP 源路由功能：Cisco 设备使用 `no ip source-route` 命令，Linux 系统设置 `net.ipv4.conf.all.accept_source_route=0`，Windows 系统将注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\DisableIPSourceRouting` 设为 2。同时确保边界 ACL 过滤源路由选项（IP Option 3）的数据包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0510","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0510","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0510.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8d306744aeef0a134e581249fd492603b0e6795d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5f97-65cc-4xfc/GHSA-5f97-65cc-4xfc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0510.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83214/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0764.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0754","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0754.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0504","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 本地用户账户默认空密码权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在默认、空值、空白或缺失密码的本地用户或管理员账户漏洞，攻击者可通过枚举或暴力破解等方式利用空密码或默认密码直接登录目标系统，获取系统控制权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击者可借助 Metasploit 等工具框架中的认证用户代码执行模块实施远程利用，无需额外认证绕过。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0504"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.193","remediation":"为所有 Windows NT 本地用户和管理员账户设置复杂密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符）。启用本地安全策略中的密码复杂度要求和账户锁定阈值（如 5 次失败即锁定 30 分钟）。通过组策略禁用 Guest 账户，并定期审计所有本地账户密码状态。对于 Windows Server，可在安全模板中启用密码必须满足复杂性要求策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0504","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16374","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0504.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0504","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0504.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0504.json","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/remote-exploits/20991.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce70cbcf8165046f2229cbe0d9f53c47bf63ece0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4cc2-25hc-9x3v/GHSA-4cc2-25hc-9x3v.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_login_as_users.nasl","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/cve_2_MSF_exploit_Mapping/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/dradis/dradis-nexpose/blob/fe9333a24a7a643ff8ddf64588baac4a9062fc0a/templates/full_vulnerability.sample"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0754.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0753","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0753.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0503","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 账户可猜测密码漏洞","description":"Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统中存在用户账户密码强度不足的漏洞，本地用户或管理员账户若设置了弱口令或默认密码，攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击等方���获取系统访问权限。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 等版本，允许已获得本地访问权限的攻击者提升权限或横向移动。建议使用强密码策略并启用账户锁定机制以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0503"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.083","remediation":"通过本地安全策略（secpol.msc）启用密码必须符合复杂性要求策略，设置密码长度最小值至少 8 个字符，密码最长使用期限不超过 90 天，并启用账户锁定阈值（5 次无效登录后锁定 30 分钟）。对于已停服的 Windows NT/2000 系统，建议迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署 Active Directory 组策略统一实施密码策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0503","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0503.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0503","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0503.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c6